# Pixel.Drift — 3D Racing Game Implementation Plan

## Overview

**Pixel.Drift** is the 7th game in the DreamRealm Games Hub. It's a 3D arcade racing game built entirely in the browser using **Three.js**. No backend, no external assets — everything is procedurally generated or programmatically modelled in JavaScript.

The player races a car around progressively complex tracks. The track starts as a simple oval and evolves into a multi-chicane circuit with hairpins and banked curves. Obstacles appear from **Level 31** onward in three flavors.

