### Engine Architecture

```
┌─ Scene Setup ─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Three.js Scene, PerspectiveCamera (chase cam),        │
│  WebGLRenderer (antialiased), directional + ambient    │
│  lights, fog for depth effect                          │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ Track Generation ────────────────────────────────────┐
│  generateTrack(level) → array of CenterlinePoints      │
│  Level 1-5:   Simple oval (8 control points)           │
│  Level 6-15:  Two chicanes added                       │
│  Level 16-29: Hairpin corners, variable-width straights│
│  Level 30+:   Full circuit with banked S-curves        │
│                                                        │
│  Track mesh built with THREE.TubeGeometry along        │
│  CatmullRomCurve3 centerline. Road width = 12 units.   │
│  Track walls (invisible collision planes) on each side │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ Car Model (Programmatic) ────────────────────────────┐
│  No external GLB/OBJ files. Built from BoxGeometry     │
│  primitives grouped into a THREE.Group:                │
│  - Body (wide flat box, cyan tinted)                   │
│  - Cabin (narrower box on top)                         │
│  - 4x Wheels (CylinderGeometry, rotated 90°)          │
│  - Headlights (PointLight, yellow glow)                │
│  Car group follows track centerline tangent            │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ Physics (Custom Arcade) ─────────────────────────────┐
│  - No rigid body engine (cannon.js), pure math         │
│  - t parameter (0–1) tracks car position along curve   │
│  - Speed: t += speed * dt                              │
│  - Steering: lateral offset from centerline (±4 units)│
│  - Wheel spin animation: wheel rotation += speed * dt  │
│  - Wall bounce: if |offset| > halfWidth → reflect      │
│  - Lap detection: t wraps around 0–1                   │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ Camera ──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Chase camera: positioned behind & above car           │
│  camera.position = carPos - tangent*8 + up*4          │
│  camera.lookAt( carPos + tangent*2 )                   │
│  Smooth lerp each frame (lerp factor 0.1)             │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

