### Track Generation Detail

```js
function generateTrack(level) {
    // Returns array of Vector3 control points for CatmullRomCurve3
    // Level 1: simple oval — 8 points forming ellipse
    // Each level adds: more control points, sharper turns, varied radii
    // From level 16: introduce chicane pairs (S-shape insertions)
    // From level 25: hairpin (180° reversal node)
    // Track is always a closed loop (curve.closed = true)
}
```

Track surface: `THREE.TubeGeometry(curve, segments, radius, radialSegments)`  
Road markings: dashed `LineSegments` along centerline  
Environment: flat plane (`PlaneGeometry`) as ground, colored `#0a0a1a`  
Skybox: solid dark color with subtle fog (`scene.fog = new THREE.FogExp2(...)`)  

