### Level Progression

| Level Range | Track Shape | Lap Time Target | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1–5 | Simple oval | 30s | Just gas + steer |
| 6–15 | 2 chicanes | 40s | First real corners |
| 16–29 | Hairpins + chicanes | 55s | Technical racing |
| 30+ | Full complex circuit | 70s+ | Obstacles spawn too |

**Level Up Trigger:** Complete N laps (N = 1 + floor(level/5)). Max laps per level = 10.  
**Speed Scaling:** Base speed 0.0008 (t/ms), + 0.00003 per level, capped at 0.003.

