## Verification Plan

### Automated (Browser Subagent)
1. Navigate to `localhost:3000/games/pixel-drift/index.html`
2. Click Play, verify 3D scene loads (car + track visible)
3. Press W → car accelerates, camera follows
4. Complete one lap → Level 2 loads correctly
5. Navigate to Level 31 (via JS console `GAME.level = 31`) → verify obstacles spawn
6. Hit a solid obstacle → verify HP decreases
7. Hit a slow obstacle → verify speed drop
8. HP = 0 → verify game over screen

### Manual
- Mobile touchscreen D-pad
- Visual quality check (neon glow, car model looks arcade-appropriate)
